All Implemented Interfaces:
com.mobius.vdrapi.IHasConnectionState, IHasDescription, IHasName, IListFactory, INode
public class ReportNode
extends ListFactoryNode
implements IHasDescription, IHasName

A ReportNode is created by a SessionFactory of type SessionFactoryType.Report, and represents a report located on a document server. It contains a list of versions and data describing the report.
